    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/012a818aea2ad02c39c2128d37c060a2.avif?t=1750545167\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras_big/012a818aea2ad02c39c2128d37c060a2.avif?t=1750545167 width=800 height=143 /></span>In 'Chosen of God', you take on the role of the young shepherd David, destined to become King. In a world filled with danger and challenges, you must face formidable enemies, from giants to entire armies, using your combat skills and strategy to prevail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a dynamic and thrilling gameplay experience, combining hack-and-slash elements with RPG mechanics. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features:</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/1f93ff6e4b4dcc13236836642b6682da.avif?t=1750545167\" width=610 height=91 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/812b25eba895213c5728540921de3153.poster.avif?t=1750545167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/812b25eba895213c5728540921de3153.webm?t=1750545167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fluid Combat</strong>: Execute devastating combos, dodge enemy attacks, perform parries, and block blows with precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aerial Dominance</strong>: Launch your enemies into the air and continue the fight mid-air.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/3994ed6fdbfba53bf0cab21b2f8a4757.avif?t=1750545167\" width=610 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/be02751122d5618160c3bd44b35e6b69.poster.avif?t=1750545167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/be02751122d5618160c3bd44b35e6b69.webm?t=1750545167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant Ascent</strong>: Improve your attributes and skills to become an unstoppable warrior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Arsenal</strong>: Unlock new weapons and upgrade existing ones to adapt to any challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/eaf4dc77cff2e6211d4e9f1c954be45b.avif?t=1750545167\" width=610 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/a3c71cf2029d2458745a3e268c8909ac.poster.avif?t=1750545167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/a3c71cf2029d2458745a3e268c8909ac.webm?t=1750545167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overcome Obstacles</strong>: Climb cliffs, jump chasms, swim, and overcome any obstacle in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover and Conquer</strong>: Collect valuable items and interact with the environment to uncover great rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vases and Urns</strong>: By breaking vases, urns, or other fragile objects, players can find coins, gems, potions, or even keys that unlock secret areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/5b09db949d97b23d117fe101bfedfadb.avif?t=1750545167\" width=610 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/820c985d8b7b2fb58b5aa6c02159d4ef.poster.avif?t=1750545167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317930/extras/820c985d8b7b2fb58b5aa6c02159d4ef.webm?t=1750545167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power of the Anointed</strong>: Unleash the power of the anointed and dominate the battlefield with time on your side.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Liberation and Justice</strong>: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue innocent prisoners and free the oppressed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recover stolen livestock and treasures.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faith and Devotion</strong>: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy pagan idols and purify the land. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect God's altars.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special abilities</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harp</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Devastating Arrow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow Flurry</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whirlwind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coup de Grâce</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Judgment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Downward Strike</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mass</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
